{"tid":57753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你真係愛我，就發射啦","createTime":"2016-12-28T09:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T10:20:41.000Z","uid":49648,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d053c7c10206bae2b7c02a286009c539587fe89c","tid":57753,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPxm565m2218fLSGkxA7HNi9VUzM5ve853d1G23NXwR9o?filename=T8T0gDB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT8T0gDB.jpg&h=fa896ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n導演冇話改 <br />\n<br />\n談到她在無綫劇《巾幗梟雄III之諜血長天》中的對白「如果你真係愛我，就發射啦」獲網友瘋傳，她為此感到高興：「嗰日做冬，阿妹就問我點解要講呢個字，點解唔講發炮？其實拍嗰時都好Rush，導演冇話改我都就冇諗過要改。」非常搞笑。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27302232e7febbfdd5f0ba155f12aec8fa813289","tid":57753,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T10:20:41.000Z","msg":"講慣左，無計。<br />\n<br />\n射啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}